channel.title: Comments on: Launch: Around The World For Free

item.title: By: gazingeyes
item.dc:creator: gazingeyes
item.description: I think this is fantastic! I love how easy it is to watch. I am also using jokersupdates.com which has the links posted to further make it easier to navigate the webisodes, maps and all the pictures, tweets, etc. Kudo's for making this a great experience and an easy way to keep up with Jeff as he travels around the world!

item.title: By: Maggie
item.dc:creator: Maggie
item.description: You guys did a great job on the website. Really easy to use and understand. Love it. Thanks for all your work. The experience wouldn't be the same without the website.
